content: can't believe the nerve of some people

photo.alt:
screenshot of text messages where the sender is named "Roommate".

roommate: hey amy i noticed the rent was due a couple days ago and you still haven’t venmo’d me your share. can you send it to me when you have time?  

me: It's a real shame that this is the world we find ourselves in now.

me: One so sharply divided by calendars and economic disparity that we can't even share the love of our apartment together without a need to settle scores.
